{% from "components/united-kingdom-national-insurance-number-view/macro.njk" import unitedKingdomNationalInsuranceNumberView %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<dl>
  <dt>National Insurance Number</dt>
  <dd>{{ unitedKingdomNationalInsuranceNumberView({ value: "sample-value", label: "National Insurance Number" }) }}</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>two prefix letters, six digits, and a suffix letter (A, B, C, or D) — e.g. AB123456A; the letters D, F, I, Q, U, V and the prefix-2 letter O are excluded.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Insurance_number">National Insurance Number</a>.</p>
